    "notes": ""
  },
  {
    "index": 58,
    "texts": [
      "GAUNTLET",
      "TRACK",
      "It is railway arrangement where Two separate tracks",
      "Overlap and share the same formation , with rails",
      "interlaced without using point and switches, such that",
      "Only one train can pass through the restricted section",
      "at a time.( at bridges, tunnels, platforms)."
