      "allowing trains to move straight",
      "across or switches diagonally",
      "between intersecting tracks."
    ],
    "notes": ""
  },
  {
    "index": 62,
    "texts": [
      "RAILWAY",
      "TRAINLE (WYE)",
      "A Triangle is a special track",
